body:
All our released object detection models have frozen graph, what you are looking for is not frozen graph but a different model trained with tflite.
Not sure which mobile net version are you looking for, but I guess this [ssdlite mobilenev v2](http://download.tensorflow.org/models/object_detection/ssdlite_mobilenet_v2_coco_2018_05_09.tar.gz) works for you?
